title: 'Comfortable and good quality'
body: I was initially sceptical about buying these chairs from Amazon. But after i got the chairs, I'm really glad I did. The chairs are comfortable and of good quality. The installation was also really easy to do and the tools to install were given with the product. Also the seller was personally in touch with me incase i had any issues.
